<plot>Plagued with chronic insomnia, Joe McDoake's sleep is disrupted by such minor annoyances as his wife's snoring, a dripping faucet, street noise, and the wind. He allows himself to be treated by a specialist, but when even the doctor's treatments prove ineffective, Joe resorts to drastic methods to solve his problem.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503828</url></doc>
